comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-07T10:24:45.552Z",maintainer-agent,"Audit waves 1-5 complete: 71 OPEN backlog items created + AC backfilled + dedupe sweep clean (0 dups) + validate/health ok + 2 ADRs recorded. Proceeding to consolidation, commit, PR, bot-review loop."
  "2026-06-07T10:45:40.829Z",maintainer-agent,"Continuation note: live GitHub check on 2026-06-07 found no open PRs and no PR attached to branch pm/forward-backlog-rebuild-and-adr-gaps-2026-06-07, despite the pending PR-review loop language. Local branch is clean with commit ee897da3 ahead of origin/main. Bootstrap before publish passed: npm install -g . and pnpm build."
  "2026-06-07T10:46:53.162Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence before PR publish: npm install -g . ok; pnpm build passed; pnpm changelog:pm left CHANGELOG.md unchanged; pnpm changelog:pm:check passed; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift returned ok:true with history_drift ok and known resolution metadata warnings on older closed items; pm health --check-only --summary --json returned ok:true. GitHub live state: no open PRs before push."
  "2026-06-07T10:59:34.934Z",maintainer-agent,"CI fix evidence: PR #143 Gates (static) failed in pnpm security:scan because pm-97yv contained local release-operation details: an absolute home path and shell-token note. Sanitized pm-97yv body via pm update and redacted the historical literals with pm history-redact; redaction verify_ok true. Local verification after fix: pnpm security:scan passed; direct changelog generate --check passed; pnpm contracts:check passed; pnpm quality:static passed; npm pack --dry-run passed; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift ok:true with history_drift ok and the known older resolution warnings."
  "2026-06-07T11:12:29.122Z",maintainer-agent,"Post-merge evidence: PR #143 merged to main at 2606efd34d60a846f359c17b150e3c09faaca46a. Final PR checks green: CI build/typecheck/static/compat/smokes/coverage/runtime matrix, Docs, CodeQL, CodeRabbit status. Telemetry status shows enabled=true, last_successful_flush_at=2026-06-07T11:11:37.299Z, queue valid; pm health ok:true. Sentry CLI issue list returned live pm-cli unresolved issue data, confirming Sentry access/context."
