close_reason: "Completed: rebuilt the living forward backlog and ADR coverage, published PR #143, fixed the static security-scan issue in pm-97yv, verified all GitHub checks and reviewer state, merged to main, and confirmed telemetry plus Sentry visibility."
plan_mode: executing
plan_scope: Rebuild the living forward backlog (features/stories/tasks/chores/issues/improvements/ideas/goals) + ADR gaps across all capability epics; no source/code/docs changes (tracking-only); all new backlog items OPEN; new ADRs closed Decisions with final changelog regen.
