plan_steps[10]{id,order,title,status,created_at,updated_at,body,owner,evidence,completed_at}:
  plan-step-001,1,"Audit CLI command surface & schema/config (epics pm-mpbb, pm-8jdc)",completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:51.388Z","2026-06-07T10:25:05.833Z","Deep-audit src/cli, command surface, completion, contracts, config/schema/governance/settings-validator vs tracked work; create OPEN forward backlog under pm-mpbb & pm-8jdc; verify pm-haak schema-leak fix is real.",audit-cli-schema-agent,"Done. audit-cli-schema-agent: 8 items under pm-mpbb/pm-8jdc + audit Story pm-srex; verified pm-haak FIXED (SettingsPersistSourceSnapshot).","2026-06-07T10:25:05.833Z"
  plan-step-002,2,"Audit MCP server + SDK/extensions/packages (epics pm-5k4v, pm-ugqx)",completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:51.648Z","2026-06-07T10:25:06.053Z","Deep-audit src/mcp, src/sdk/cli-contracts, src/core/extensions, src/core/packages, packages/*; create OPEN forward backlog under pm-5k4v & pm-ugqx.",audit-platform-agent,"Done. audit-platform-agent: 16 items under pm-5k4v/pm-ugqx + audit Story pm-b4cp; flagged MCP ping (pm-lold) + FlagDefinition list-field (pm-ltbr).","2026-06-07T10:25:06.053Z"
  plan-step-003,3,"Audit storage/history + search/semantic (epics pm-o2kc, pm-ydp6)",completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:51.912Z","2026-06-07T10:25:06.284Z","Deep-audit src/core/store, history, item, fs, checkpoint, search, vector snapshot; create OPEN forward backlog under pm-o2kc & pm-ydp6.",audit-data-agent,"Done. audit-data-agent: 16 items under pm-o2kc/pm-ydp6 + audit Story pm-34gb; flagged gc-embeddings pending-refresh gap (pm-3b1t) + eval-harness re-file (pm-u8n5).","2026-06-07T10:25:06.284Z"
  plan-step-004,4,Audit observability/telemetry/health (epic pm-5oj5),completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:52.140Z","2026-06-07T10:25:06.499Z","Deep-audit src/core/telemetry, diagnostics, sentry, health/validate/stats commands + live telemetry stack + Sentry; create OPEN forward backlog under pm-5oj5.",audit-observability-agent,"Done. audit-observability-agent: 10 items under pm-5oj5 + audit Story pm-lzrq; live telemetry+Sentry observed healthy; flagged retry-exhaustion visibility (pm-irc7). No secrets in items.","2026-06-07T10:25:06.499Z"
  plan-step-005,5,Audit docs/onboarding/release/CI + tests/coverage (epic pm-u9d0),completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:52.355Z","2026-06-07T10:25:06.754Z","Deep-audit docs/*, .github/workflows, scripts, tests/*, coverage config, release automation; create OPEN forward backlog under pm-u9d0.",audit-docs-tests-agent,"Done. audit-docs-tests-agent: 16 items under pm-u9d0 + audit Story pm-5dbn; flagged CodeQL float-tag (pm-ji5c) + ARCHITECTURE/docs drift.","2026-06-07T10:25:06.754Z"
  plan-step-006,6,Record ADR gaps as closed Decisions under pm-m2u1,completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:52.589Z","2026-06-07T10:25:06.985Z","From agent recommendations + recent decisions, record any architectural decisions not yet in the 27-ADR log; closed Decisions => regen changelog at end.",orchestrator,"Done. Recorded 2 ADRs: pm-7sq6 (coverage governance), pm-cc04 (agent self-repair via remediation registry). ADR log now 29.","2026-06-07T10:25:06.985Z"
  plan-step-007,7,"Consolidate: dedupe-audit, validate, reindex, health; enrich milestone roadmap",completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:52.824Z","2026-06-07T10:25:07.216Z","Run pm run dedupe-audit, pm validate, pm run reindex, pm health; cancel/merge any cross-agent duplicates; enrich pm-doxj roadmap + link new sub-epics; seed release-monitoring reminder/event.",orchestrator,"Done. Dedupe sweep clean (0 dups); validate history_drift ok, health ok:true; AC backfilled on 66 items; milestone note + release reminder pm-7zs0 added.","2026-06-07T10:25:07.216Z"
  plan-step-008,8,Commit + push + open descriptively-named PR,completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:53.051Z","2026-06-07T10:47:39.007Z",Commit all .agents/pm additions with detailed message; push branch; open PR (specific name reflecting the audit + backlog rebuild).,orchestrator,"Pushed branch pm/forward-backlog-rebuild-and-adr-gaps-2026-06-07 and opened PR #143: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/143","2026-06-07T10:47:39.007Z"
  plan-step-009,9,AI-bot review loop until zero findings,completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:53.292Z","2026-06-07T11:06:10.397Z",Trigger @codex review + /gemini review + @gemini-code-assist; wait; address every finding; re-trigger after each push; loop until all bots report no findings; keep all GitHub checks green.,orchestrator,"PR #143 review loop complete on latest commit 49a6d9b7: all GitHub checks green (CI build, typecheck, static, compat, smokes, coverage, runtime matrix; Docs; CodeQL; CodeRabbit status). Thread-aware review scan found zero review_threads. Bot limitations recorded: Gemini quota, Codex connector unavailable, Sourcery weekly diff-character rate limit/skipped, CodeRabbit skipped substantive review because 158 files exceeds 150-file limit; no actionable reviewer findings remained.","2026-06-07T11:06:10.397Z"
  plan-step-010,10,Merge to main + verify Sentry + telemetry real-time data,completed,"2026-06-07T09:53:53.580Z","2026-06-07T11:12:28.899Z",Merge PR; return to main; confirm Sentry shows recent helpful data and telemetry stack logged all actions with real-time data.,orchestrator,"Merged PR #143 at 2026-06-07T11:11:42Z as merge commit 2606efd34d60a846f359c17b150e3c09faaca46a; local checkout is main aligned with origin/main. Post-merge checks: gh pr checks all green; pm telemetry status enabled with last_successful_flush_at 2026-06-07T11:11:37.299Z and queue valid; pm telemetry stats showed recent command events; pm health --check-only --summary --json ok:true; sentry issue list returned live pm-cli issues via authenticated CLI.","2026-06-07T11:12:28.899Z"
